text: The 2021 Icelandic parliamentary election elected members of the Althing was held on 25 September 2021. ==Polling== D = Independence Party, V = Left-Green Movement, S = Social Democratic Alliance, M = Centre Party, B = Progressive Party, P = Pirate Party, F = People's Party, C = Reform Party, J = Socialist Party. ==Notes== ==References== Category:2020s in Iceland Category:2021 elections in Europe Category:September 2021 events
title: 2021 Icelandic parliamentary election
